.TH svctool 8
.SH NAME
svctool \- IndiMail/indimail-mta Service Configuration Tool

.SH SYNOPSYS
.B svctool
[
.I options
]

.SH DESCRIPTION

\fBsvctool\fR is a shell frontend for configuring IndiMail services, configuring
\fBIndiMail(7)\fR, taking backups of configuration and data. All services are configured to
run under \fBsupervise(8)\fR. \fBsupervise(8)\fR itself gets started by \fBsvscan(8)\fR.
You can install \fBsvscan(8)\fR to be started by the system using
the command \fBsvctool --config=add-boot\fR.

\fBsvctool\fR requires root privilege to run.

